reviewText:
They don't have a half-star, so one star will have to do.
Move along to something else.
We turned this off after about half an hour. What started out to be a good story turned into a soft porn movie, I really wish the content would be disclosed on rated and unrated movies on Prime.
Disjointed and simply not believable...........sorry.  Even James Earl Jones couldn't save this one.
Good acting and story line.  Well worth watching.  As always, James Earl Jones did a great job.
Being a musician, I couldn't watch all of this movie.  The violinist doesn't even know how to properly hold a violin and a bow.
This is an excellent Inspiring movie,Samuuel Ball rules as a struggling musician in the subways of New York. It's amust see!!!!
